			"body": "## Summary\n\n- Adds a new `--mode` flag to the `xagent mcp` command that supports two modes:\n  - `container` (default): For agents managed by xagent inside Docker containers\n  - `external`: For external agents not managed by xagent\n\n- External mode provides `create_task` and `get_task` tools for agents to create and retrieve tasks\n\n## Usage\n\n```bash\n# External mode (new)\nxagent mcp --mode external --server http://localhost:8080\n\n# Container mode (existing behavior, default)\nxagent mcp --mode container --server <url> --task <id> --workspace <name>\n```\n\n## Test plan\n\n- [x] Unit tests for external server tools pass\n- [x] All existing tests pass\n- [ ] Manual testing with Claude Code using external mode",
